text.div: map "http://termx.health/fhir/StructureMap/SoftwareXPerson2Patient" = "SoftwareXPerson2Patient" conceptmap "http://taltech.ee/ConceptMap/person-to-patient" { prefix s = "src" prefix t = "dst" s:M - t:male s:F - t:female s:U - t:unknown } uses "https://taltech.ee/termx/StructureDefinition/SoftwareXPerson" alias Person as source uses "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/Patient" alias Patient as target group example(source Person : Person, target Patient : Patient) { Person -> Patient then { Person -> Patient.id = uuid() as uuid7 "rule_31"; } "rule_30"; Person -> Patient then { Person -> Patient.identifier = create('Identifier') as a then { Person -> a.system = ('https://fhir.ee/sid/pid/est/ni') as constant8 "const_34"; Person.code as b -> a.value = b "dset_35"; } "rule_33"; } "rule_32"; Person -> Patient then { Person -> Patient.name = create('HumanName') as a then { Person.lastname as b -> a.family = b "dset_38"; Person.firstname as c -> a.given = c "dset_39"; } "rule_37"; } "rule_36"; Person -> Patient then { Person.gender as a -> Patient.gender = translate(a, '#http://taltech.ee/ConceptMap/person-to-patient', 'code') as translate15 "translate_41"; } "rule_40"; Person -> Patient then { Person.birthdate as a -> Patient.birthDate = a "dset_43"; } "rule_42"; }
